## Limitations

The findings are based on publicly available information and may not capture all aspects of Biles' personal coping strategies. Additionally, the information is subject to the interpretations and biases of the sources. Personal interviews or direct statements from Biles would provide a more comprehensive understanding of her experiences and coping mechanisms.